psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher.listener

Interface FeatureEvidenceEnricherListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AliasesChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, AnnotationsChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, EnricherListener<FeatureEvidence>, EventListener, FeatureChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, FeatureEnricherListener<FeatureEvidence>, FeatureEvidenceChangeListener, IdentifiersChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, ParametersChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>, XrefsChangeListener<FeatureEvidence>
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface FeatureEvidenceEnricherListener
extends FeatureEnricherListener<FeatureEvidence>, FeatureEvidenceChangeListener
    An extension of the FeatureChangeListener with specific methods related to the process of enriching. Each method will be fired after the change has been made to the feature.
    Since:
    13/06/13
